sect1.sect2:
    Introduction to SPIRV-Headers



      The SPIRV-Headers package contains headers that
allow for applications to the SPIR-V language and instruction set with
Vulkan. SPIR-V is a binary intermediate language for representing graphical
shader stages and compute kernels for multiple Khronos APIs, including
OpenGL and Vulkan.


